cloudy; Los Angeles 70 fair; Phoenix 98 partly cloudy; Salt Lake
City 73 fair; San Diego 73 fair; San Francisco 60 fair; Seattle 62
fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 66 fair; Toronto 64 fair.
