<2ND_LINE>AM-Digest Briefs,0878</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: This package does not contain the following items from the
News Digest: ATLANTA _ CVN--Convention Overview; ATLANTA _
CVN--Orderly Convention; ATLANTA _The 1960 Strategy; MEMPHIS _
